TEXT ALIGNMENT

1.When a text is displayed in a webpage the default alignment is to the left

2.In Bootstap text alignment can be adjusted using the Bootstrap text alignment feature.


TEXT ALIGNMENT EXAMPLES:

text-start:Align to the left.

text-center:Align to the center.

text-end: Align to the right.

EXAMPLE 1: TEXT ALIGN TO THE RIGHT

<p class="text-end">

...

</p>


EXAMPLE 2:TEXT ALIGN TO THE CENTER

<p class="text-center"?

...

</p>

